entries.journal_entry_description: Jeridel has begged you to spare their life. Jeridel also offered you more credits if you can find out what happened to their brother. Apparently their brother is the lead creature handler for the facility. He hasn't come home in three days. Find out what happened to him and report back.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: The creatures are contained on the third and lowest level. Search for anything that might lead to the whereabouts of the missing brother.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Find the Missing Brother On the Third Level
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You found Jenson's Datapad. You should read it to find clues as to what happened.
entries.task01_message_box_text: If anyone finds this, please tell Jeridel of my fate. I am Jenson, lead creature handler for this lab. Something has gone wrong, and the creatures are loose. The Engineered Acklay attacked me when I tried to feed it, and since then, I have been slowly bleeding to death down here.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You should track down and kill the creature that killed Jenson.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Now that you have avenged Jeridel's brother, return to Jeridel.
